Package: hdfsc
Version: 0.1-2
Title: HDFS-based connections for R and HDFS-related file operations (Hadoop Distributed File System)
Author: Simon Urbanek <Simon.Urbanek@r-project.org>
Maintainer: Simon Urbanek <Simon.Urbanek@r-project.org>
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0), methods
Imports: rJava
Description: This package provides connections that can be used to interface HDFS files as well as tools to manipulate the Hadoop Distributed File System.
License: GPL-2 | GPL-3
URL: http://www.rforge.net/hdfsc
